name: Alien Brooch
description:
This unique brooch is crafted from polymer clay then finished with swirly 'engravings' and a patina like coat of paint. Her hair is a bright spray of silver, green and pink stalks. She is a one of a kind, lovely adornment to your lapel, bag, hat, etc.

2" x 2"

name: Happy Zombie Doll Box
description: She stands 6" tall and about 3.5" wide. This is a very eye catching trinket box, which stands on three wooden feet, the chest has a brass opening and has a glossy gold interior to hide away treasures. The Zombie head has tight little knot hair, the overall color is red, but the rubbed on gold ink gives it an aged antique look and also the 'zombie' look to the face (I think). One of my faves, thanks for looking.

name: Little Lizard Guy Box
description:
He wasn't really planned this way, but he looks like a lizard to me! Handcrafted from polymer clay with glass ball eyes, painted with a mottled green, orange and black, he is mounted on a little paper mache box and finished with a collar of matte gold colored wire. The box is painted to compliment and has added 3d paint decorations.

A bit less than 3" all and about 2" wide.

name: Tiny Transylvania Trinket Treasure Box
description: Tiny: 2" high and/or across, with a lot of presence. The face is made from a mold of a face I sculpted, I was happy that even the fangs molded well! It is a totally unique little paper mache box, decorated with ink stamped vintage faces, painted with glitter paint and 3d paint, the eyes and teeth also have a touch of glitter.

name: Super Chunky Canvas
description: Hmmm where to begin...this is a OoaK piece measuring approx 6" x 8" and 3" thick. The base canvas is painted red, there is a nailed heart, with a star and face mounted on it. The layers of paint and adornment are too numerous to detail, but include a little imp face, a resin teardrop, nails and beads on top, you'll find something new in it each time you look. The face is crafted from polymer clay and has a wise expression, a slightly antique finish contrasts dramatically with the bold and colorful setting.
